openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Catracker
  version: 0.1
  description: Catracker
paths:
  /ttnhttp:
    post:
      operationId: incomingEventTtn
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/definitions/TTNEvent'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Created
  /kpn:
    post:
      operationId: incomingEventKpn
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/definitions/KPNEventRecord'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Created
  /paths/{device}:
    get:
      operationId: pathForDevice
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: device
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/DevicePath'

servers:
  - url: http://host
components:
  schemas:
    DevicePath:
      type: object
      required:
        - description
        - positions
        - lastSeen
      properties:
        description:
          type: string
        lastSeen:
          type: number
        positions:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            required:
              - latitude
              - longitude
              - battery
            properties:
              latitude:
                type: number
                format: double
              longitude:
                type: number
                format: double
              battery:
                type: number
    KPNEventRecord:
      type: object
      properties:
        bn:
          type: string
        bt:
          type: number
        v:
          type: number
        vs:
          type: string
        n:
          type: string
    TTNEvent:
      type: object
      required:
        - app_id
        - dev_id
        - hardware_serial
        - port
        - counter
        - payload_fields
        - metadata
      properties:
        app_id:
          type: string
        dev_id:
          type: string
        hardware_serial:
          type: string
        counter:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        payload_fields:
          type: object
          required:
            - accuracy
            - capacity
            - gnss_fix
            - latitude
            - longitude
            - temperature
            - voltage
          properties:
            accuracy:
              type: integer
              format: int32
            capacity:
              type: number
            gnss_fix:
              type: boolean
            latitude:
              type: number
              format: double
            longitude:
              type: number
              format: double
            port:
              type: integer
              format: int32
            temperature:
              type: integer
              format: int32
            voltage:
              type: number
        metadata:
          type: object
          required:
            - time
            - frequency
            - modulation
            - data_rate
            - coding_rate
            - gateways
          properties:
            time:
              type: string
              format: date-time
            frequency:
              type: number
            modulation:
              type: string
            data_rate:
              type: string
            coding_rate:
              type: string
            gateways:
              type: array
              items:
                type: object
                required:
                  - gtw_id
                  - time
                  - channel
                  - rssi
                  - snr
                properties:
                  gtw_id:
                    type: string
                  time:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
                  channel:
                    type: integer
                    format: int32
                  rssi:
                    type: integer
                    format: int32
                  snr:
                    type: number
        downlink_url:
          type: string
